data.description: You will appreciate the easy living this townhouse has to offer. Large first floor master bedroom with bathroom access and walk-in closet. First floor laundry near the master bedroom for added convenience. The living room is spacious with an open concept to the kitchen and dining area. Sliders off of the dining area open to a deck. Upstairs you'll find the second bedroom and a private bathroom. The basement features a family room, bar, and bathroom. Ample storage space exists in a partially finished room that could be completed as a third bedroom downstairs. Finished basement square footage is approximate.
